        "action": "Give Class D License Holders Class C1 and Class C License Holders D1 Entitlement",
        "additional_details": "Making these changes would encourage drivers of different classes to working in areas not previously open to them with out additional costly training.\r\n\r\nA Class D driver can drive a vehicle twice the weight of a Class C1 at present.",
        "background": "Give Class D License Holders Class C1 Entitlement and Class C License Holders D1 Entitlement.\r\n\r\nI Propose that Class D(PCV) License Holders should be given Class C1(7.5t LGV) entitlement.\r\n\r\nAnd that Class C(LGV) License Holders should be given CLass D1(minibus) entitlement.",
